Text: followup to telephone conversation of Mr Kean Thank you for your call I am looking forward to working for you I will be available as of June I will have the writing samples and resume ready for you on Monday March Should I fax it to you Also my dissertation is quite lengthy Would you like for me to forward you one chapter or just a couple pages As discussed I will be available to come down to Houston between March and April More snow as in inches is expected today and tomorrow Im only Pretty soon I will be buried in it since its snow upon snow HELP I look forward to seeing you again Regards Amy
